"buffer passed to the **notify_new** callback is guaranteed to be aligned on "
"a 8-byte boundary. The minimum supported size for said buffer can be "
"specified using **min_event_size**. WMI drivers that still use the "
"deprecated **notify** callback can still set **min_event_size** to 0 in "
"order to signal that they support WMI events which provide no event data."
